=======================================
Offline features extraction
=======================================

- Compilation
$ make

---------------------------------------

- Usage:
$ ./rwthfeat 
Usage: ./rwthfeat img.pgm w_size [-vr]

---------------------------------------

- Example: offline features extraction using a sliding window of width
           5 pixels   

$ ./rwthfeat pi.pgm 5 > pi.fea

- Example: offline features extraction using a sliding window of width
           5 pixels with vertical repositioning

$ ./rwthfeat pi.pgm 5 -vr > pi.vr.fea

  *Note that you might want to project each window using PCA!
